name: CleanNFT
description: I painted this digital animation to raise awareness about NFTs sustainability and the climate crisis we are pretending to care about. I had refused to participate in any NFTs on the ETH blockchain hoping one day it will become state-of-proof and sure, I have missed on several opportunities until I heard of hic et nunc, on which I minted my first NFT artwork on the tezos net and am now minting this one and I thank all those who have been of support proving that it's never too late. Thank you!
